{
  "argument_loc": "Unspecified",
  "description": "Subtracts numbers or arrays from each another, negates a number. For arrays also see [[deleteAt]] and [[deleteRange]].\n{{Feature|arma3|In Arma 3 it is possible to subtract nested arrays.}}",
  "effect_loc": "Unspecified",
  "examples": [
    "<sqf>_result = 10 - 7; // result is 3</sqf>",
    "<sqf>\n_numA = 4;\n_numB = -_numA; // result is -4\n_numB = -_numB; // result is  4\n</sqf>",
    "<sqf>_result = [1, 2, 2, player, \"String\"] - [2, player, player, \"String\"]; // _result is [1]</sqf>",
    "<sqf>_result = [0, [0], [[0]]] - [0]; // [[0], [[0]]]</sqf>",
    "<sqf>\n_result = [0, [0], [[0]]] - [[0]];\t\t// [0, [[0]]]\t- Since {{arma3}}\n_result = [0, [0], [[0]]] - [[[0]]];\t// [0, [0]]\t\t- Since {{arma3}}\n</sqf>"
  ],
